Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.20,0:01:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创界山是分了七层\N由神仙居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打倒支配这座山的\N邪恶帝王多恶达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、火美子和武一郎师傅\N一边和多恶达的魔神战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边以第七界层为目标前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四界层得到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.87,0:01:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能令炎热的第三界层\N回复原状的极寒之剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全地把它交还了亚撒姆像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.71,0:02:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令第三界层\N回复原来的和平世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,今次到第四界层了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.45,0:02:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为把灼热之剑交还胡娜拉像\N我们上了第四界层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.87,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十九话\N龙神丸飞了,飞了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪啊!雪啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷!…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,快点出去啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这里太冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之国…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如传闻一样冷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手,我不是皮草啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你,在下最怕冷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅\N你不是说过最怕热的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.92,0:03:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,冷也不行\N我对温度太敏感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心\N不要用你的巨脸贴着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很巨大,真抱歉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起此事,还是快点\N把灼热之剑交还胡娜拉像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢,赶快吧,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是颈巾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.50,0:03:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这差劲的品味是什么?\N多多路高士蒙也是个蠢材吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别投诉了\N只要打倒那个小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便要和这恶心的地说再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥,让那个叫渡的小鬼\N知道我们的可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他享受尽痛苦\N才送他进地狱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子没有了,鼻子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残恶鸟,去追他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残兄弟大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等,请问你们去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.05,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用屁股向着我说话\N我们现在去收拾渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再多给我一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股和头也一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你们的福\N今次一定可以收拾渡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以暂时请你们\N留多这里一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高士蒙\N我最讨厌做无谓的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以这人头担保\N你不是无谓的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是无谓之极啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那信任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能信任呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能、不能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只有令你们信任了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的客人有100人\N小学3年平成八年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥林匹克是第41届
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了?这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短枪郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮他人仍家常便饭\N不论何时也能自由变身的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.20,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芋川短枪郎,登场!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  很多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The great super易容师\N短枪郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N我应该说超级伟大易容师的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这家伙很怕洋文字的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.65,0:05:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋文字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说…hamburg
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等\N如果他扮成雪便能接近渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能抢夺灼热之剑\N当然刺杀的准备也万全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位只要在此\N一边吃一边等便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流水拉面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.10,0:06:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这面是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以飞象过河啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…,胡娜拉像在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了那座山便到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便到了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何可以把这么大工夫的事\N说得这么轻松?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,听到幻觉了\N这样的地方没可能有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻觉!是幻觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是渡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪\N是渡的相识吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真生外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是灼热之剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看,让我看,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.54,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个\N还是赶快去野野神殿吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大风雪也弱下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢\N但是胡娜拉像又再移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.70,0:07:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大风雪停了真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N你会有这么大的床单?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱的女孩呢\N一点点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要过这吊桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这条桥\N不是已冰封了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.63,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样\N有一点冲击也会碎散呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也非去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.64,0:08:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,拿着两把剑会很重吧\N我替你拿一把吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重少少没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.72,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点…\N我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不要跳啊\N但是我很难活动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险,是冰雹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.76,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已到地狱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.64,0:09:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛\N就算只有渡和火美子也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说这些好听话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是Oh my god呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N我…只是有点慌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条桥已完了\N那之后怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.60,0:10:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然有点远\N走别的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.01,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,我不是想怀疑你的朋友\N但是太可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎会?\N你有什么根据吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虽然说胡娜拉像移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她现在和亚撒姆重聚中\N没可能会动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却不能说一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.30,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊\N这样不是不能成为理由吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这是同样是间谍的直觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛!\N鸟先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,什么事也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅,你太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知我说得太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.85,0:11:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在把灼热之剑\N交还胡娜拉像要紧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.50,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,相信曾经出卖他的人\N始终是没可能的事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,你是雪吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是渡的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡在哪里?\N他一直也不来令我很担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪,你可以和我一起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要绕到哪里啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很远呢\N离山已这么远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题,只差少少便到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点想法子的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如放下剑休息一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是呢\N师傅,休息一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧\N我肚子饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只对吃有兴趣吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.95,0:13:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢吃东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是老实的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想吃ice-cream
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ice-cream吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么冷\N我不想想起ice-cream
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃curry rice呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下想喝热热的cream soup呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是ice-cream了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要vanilla和chocolate味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,punt cake也不错呢\N要放很多cheese
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟fish的话会很暖呢\N但这里没可能吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想吃呢\N差不多走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?怎么了?雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,什么事也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒…倒是赶快行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N这样再去一次山谷那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等啊\N古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,这是怎么一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N原来雪是有孪生姐妹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,那家伙是假扮的雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.66,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分\N那边才是假扮的,对吧,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没你办法\N她是你朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,谁才是真的呢?\N欢迎真人到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.71,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么真的雪是谁呢?\N那现在由她的朋友问问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.98,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是雪\N应该是拿着火龙之鳞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是绿色那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,雪小姐\N准备好鳞片了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.06,0:15:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在来了\N谁才是真的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有请…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越令我不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.60,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡\N没有其他方法可以分辨吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.17,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,雪受伤的时候\N我曾帮她涂药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.75,0:15:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,留有伤痕的\N便是真正的小雪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.88,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,先看这边的小雪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.70,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪处?\N师傅,不用这么近也看见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这种事不搞清楚不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.61,0:15:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错了,好\N跟着到那边的小雪给我看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?不可以看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.63,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有伤痕表示你是假的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这样,和我想的一样呢\N假的雪…是你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?有伤痕的是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替雪涂的药\N是火美子处取来的万能药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这药是可以令伤痕也消失的\N对吧,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.75,0:16:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对\N不愧是渡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你们看穿了真厉害\N我是创界山第一易容师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芋川短枪郎就是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.23,0:16:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便攻过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,雪,你拿着这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光头,光头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!\N古拿玛,雪小姐拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,是陷阱啊,快回来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能来到这里是你运气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之后便要你\N试试我的厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷神火炎剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,电话…\N那边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战-神-丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,战神丸?\N在午饭前打给你真不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋风飞弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡\N用飞龙拳让那家伙停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.95,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,飞龙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等,让在下收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边交给你了,魔幻怪光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了,渡,雪她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,去救雪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.50,0:19:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你去的,看招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.12,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样?你无从入手吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,这边交给空神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是古拿玛吗?\N看来你已加入了他们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.56,0:20:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.57,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是龙神丸飞起了一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.92,0:20:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害\N是龙神丸和空神丸的合体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸在空中飞翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,空神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,古拿玛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气了,渡\N放低雪之后,就这样开战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,去了哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.54,0:20:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐,旋风风弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,用下一招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.88,0:21:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空龙牙拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.99,0:21:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,短枪郎那个蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你的屁股人头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点用也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残兄弟大人,请原谅我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没法子吧,就这样撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然胡娜拉像\N是没有移动过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.87,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,我没有听你说话\N真的很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别理它吧,已过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.60,0:22:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,千人仙人在等着\N快点去野野神殿吧,快点!


